462
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:30,512
Menakjubkan bagaimana setiap tipe
menemukan pengagum.

463
00:39:31,480 --> 00:39:32,480
Meskipun sayang,

464
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:35,192
pengabdian Si pasti akan sia-sia.

465
00:39:44,639 --> 00:39:46,273
kau penuh perhatian,

